<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870828-0155 </DOCNO><HL> Financing Business:Stevens Graphics Corp.</HL><DD> 08/28/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> SVGINITIAL STOCK OFFERINGS (INI)STOCK MARKET, OFFERINGS (STK) </IN><TEXT>   STEVENS GRAPHICS CORP. began an initial offering of 1.3 million common shares at $12 a share. The Fort Worth, Texas, maker of printing presses said 900,000 shares are being sold by the company and the balance offered by certain stockholders. Proceeds will used to reduce debt. Eppler, Guerin andamp; Turner Inc. is the lead underwriter for the offering. </TEXT></DOC>